'''Suki''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|woman]] who attended the celebrations in [[Gadrin]] for the 200th anniversary of the [[City/Legends|city's]] founding by [[Reidi Artom]]. She and her friend [[Amaya]] went to [[Vanster Enan's Sop House]] to try to find men to party with. Amaya hooked up with a greasy man named [[Kip (Human)|Kip]], but Suki was left looking for somebody to gravitate too. She liked "bad boys."

